CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 5, 1959, pg. A2 reads: "Feature Roles - Feature roles i n the religious program, "God and Man," presented by the NAACP Youth Council, last Sunday, at Bethel AME Church, were held by, left to right: Neel Huguley [sic] Jr., soloist; Ronald Browne, narrator, and Joseph Lee, organist. The choir of St. Luke Baptist Church also participated. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Neel Huguley Jr., Ronald Browne, and Joseph Lee standing at podium in Bethel AME Church for NAACP Youth Council program
